        "collapsible_tab_E7BiDw": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What does Nitric Oxide do for my body?",
            "content": "<p>Nitric oxide helps relax and widen blood vessels, improving circulation. This supports energy, endurance, cardiovascular health, and even sexual function — especially as we age and natural NO production declines.</p>",
            "icon": "none",
            "faq_id": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_9kGwAH": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How long do I need to take Berkeley Life before I see results?",
            "content": "<p>As with all supplements, everyone will feel a difference at different speeds. There are some who notice a difference right away, and others see benefits after using the product for about a month. However, unlike most supplements you can <strong>validate</strong> that our N.O. supplements are working by using our patented Nitric Oxide Test Strip before and 90 minutes after you take the supplement.</p>",
            "icon": "none",
            "faq_id": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_C7d9Qc": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can't I get the dietary nitrates in Berkeley Life just through my diet?",
            "content": "<p>Leafy greens, beetroot, arugula, spinach and celery are all vegetables known to be high in dietary nitrates. However, nutrient density of the soil across the country makes it difficult to predict exactly how much of these greens are required daily to provide a clinically effective dose of nitrates to produce nitric oxide. In our experience, it requires more leafy greens than most people over 35 are willing or able to consume every day.</p>",
            "icon": "none",
            "faq_id": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_B974jh": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I take Berkeley Life with other medications?",
            "content": "<p>Berkeley Life is safe, well-tolerated, and has no contra-indications for medications. As always, if you are uncertain work with your healthcare provider to determine the appropriate combination of medicine and supplementation that's right for you. </p>",
            "icon": "none",
            "faq_id": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_QVB7Rq": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How long will it take to get my order?",
            "content": "<p>It depends on where you are. Orders processed before 2pm EST are shipped same day and generally will take 3-7 business days to arrive. Canadian deliveries can take anywhere from 7-16 days. Delivery details will be provided in your confirmation email.</p>",
            "icon": "none",
            "faq_id": ""
          }
        }
      },
